sequenceDiagram
  participant P as Client pump
  participant S as YoutubeSabrSession
  participant T as StreamState
  participant Y as YouTube SABR server
  P->>S: pumpOnce()
  S->>T: read player time, buffered ranges, cookie, PO token
  S->>Y: POST VideoPlaybackAbrRequest
  Y-->>S: UMP response
  S->>S: UmpReader + SabrResponseDecoder
  S->>T: ingest media + control parts
  S-->>P: collected segments
